text: WSTRN is an English West London singing group consisting of Akelle Charles, Louis Rei and Haile. They are known because of their debut song, "In2", which was released on 13 October 2015 and peaked at number 4 on the UK Singles Chart. Louis Rei was formerly known as LB, Akelle was formerly known as A-Star and is Haile's cousin.
